{"tid":374853,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"請好好珍惜會整Tiramisu 比你食嘅女朋友","createTime":"2017-08-26T05:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T09:52:06.000Z","uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41793effbf224a064270af15e1abc0039c5faa9c","tid":374853,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/131129_3f4a6455fff642ebb088c86e9d61732b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F131129_3f4a6455fff642ebb088c86e9d61732b.jpg&h=398aadc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會整Tiramisu 比你嘅女朋友代表咩？<br />\n1.佢了解你嘅喜樂，會關心同取悅你，唔係自求回<br />\n報不作付出。<br />\n2.佢有tasty,有眼界，知道咩好食咩唔好食， 唔會岸鳩鳩整舊馬拉糕。<br />\n3.佢勤力。港女好多連飯都唔識煮，淥公仔面都唔識煎隻蛋加餸。如果佢肯為你整tiramisu, 一定係佢下過一返苦工，呢份心思，係現今香港已經夠難能可貴！<br />\n4.佢唔係岸鳩鳩100磅唔夠仲串柒柒話自己肥果啲發溫雞。唔會係你繁重工作後，想食啲甜品氹下自己時同你講食甜品會肥，唔比食呢類冷血說話。<br />\n5.人人天份唔同，就算佢唔識整，而佢至少肯買一舊Tiramisu 比你食，證明佢都係個體貼女朋友。都叫過關！<br />\n咩話，你無食過女朋友嘅tiramisu⁉️你確認同件死港女仲有發展空間？"},{"pid":"5581408cbb2009d6e79e969d631743972278f060","tid":374853,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946af1e167f1173be9a00976bb8c2bbdcd0a8c06","tid":374853,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:40:55.000Z","msg":"港女只能偷偷留下負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4d1d6f0b1499decb22e983f50ea04d033bf1b4","tid":374853,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"真係陰鳩公，原來港女真係咁撚垃圾，唔煮得又唔睇得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a0f87be24516711e0b15f4d010ca8346ed2ce7","tid":374853,"uid":38970,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"識整舊爛鬼屎餅